    <dd>The encryption type to use. If you use the <code>KMS</code> encryption type, the contents of the repository will be encrypted using server-side encryption with KMSlong key stored in KMS. If you use the <code>AES256</code> encryption type, Amazon ECR uses server-side encryption with Amazon S3-managed encryption keys which encrypts the images in the repository using an AES-256 encryption algorithm.
